{"tid":925529,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情 就好似冬天沖涼咁...","createTime":"2018-12-02T20:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T22:20:48.000Z","uid":146934,"like":14,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7421e6981a9c20604a5e503d31f74d05c80ddc7","tid":925529,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:00:32.000Z","msg":"愛情 就好似冬天沖涼咁...<br />\n沖緊熱水涼嘅時候 永遠都係最舒服<br />\n就好比熱戀中嘅情侶<br />\n但你知道每次沖涼都有限期<br />\n脫離熱水嗰刻永遠係最冰冷<br />\n同樣地<br />\n每段感情都有佢嘅限期<br />\n分開之後總會感到空虛寂莫凍<br />\n所有蜜運中嘅回憶全部出哂黎<br />\n但過多陣 其實冇得沖熱水涼其實冇咩大不了<br />\n只不過係你對佢過分依賴<br />\n過五分鐘、十分鐘 <br />\n冰冷既感覺就會消散<br />\n<br />\n而毒撚就等於沖儲水式熱水爐<br />\n只能夠享受短暫快感<br />\n次次都以為有機會被愛<br />\n點知熱水用完後<br />\n就被迫返到冰冷既現實<br />\n一剎那嘅甜原來全部都係夢 係幻想<br />\n<br />\n而笑到最後嘅 永遠都係有錢裝暖氣嘅人<br />\n<br />\n人的一生就係一個不停沖涼嘅過程<br />\n<br />\n沖沖下涼突然有感而發 <br />\n打到呢度 我嘅熱水都用完了......"},{"pid":"fafed0b71e91a67b904b0609c71f3898f56fddaa","tid":925529,"uid":143152,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:03:29.000Z","msg":"好尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa1e2a5a9814402fa964ebbc91893ebef16cbb8","tid":925529,"uid":189715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:08:47.000Z","msg":"呢位兄台 你好似好撚傷"},{"pid":"bc850176fbbccf4854dfa935e46fc32521e7eacb","tid":925529,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fafed0b71e91a67b904b0609c71f3898f56fddaa","tid":925529,"uid":143152,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:03:29.000Z","msg":"好尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:09:32.000Z","msg":"真..."},{"pid":"3103d1b34963159147423724c02c3052aaa42bba","tid":925529,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fafed0b71e91a67b904b0609c71f3898f56fddaa","tid":925529,"uid":143152,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T20:03:29.000Z","msg":"好尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.